<h1 id="bookTitle" class="gr-h1 gr-h1--serif" itemprop="name">
      The Dark Side: The Inside Story of How the War on Terror Turned Into a War on American Ideals
</h1>
<h2 id="bookSeries">
</h2>

<div id="bookAuthors" class="">
