    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2980509194" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2980509194" />
    <a title="Andy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2199404-andy"><img alt="Andy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1331458678p2/2199404.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2980509194?book_show_action=true">Sep 17, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Andy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Andy" href="/user/show/2199404-andy">Andy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9780739375921" href="/book/show/3952671-the-dark-side">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2980509194" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10543556868986400556">Devastating critique of Bush/Cheney&apos;s deranged emotional response to 9/11. Clarifies not just the abject illegality and anti-Americanism of torture, but also its ineffectiveness and dangerous consequences. The book is not as tightly written as Mayer&apos;s subsequent &quot;Dark&quot; work: <br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/27833494.Dark_Money_The_Hidden_History_of_the_Billionaires_Behind_the_Rise_of_the_Radical_Right' title='Dark Money The Hidden History of the Billionaires Behind the Rise of the Radical Right by Jane Mayer' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1452601408l/27833494._SY75_.jpg' alt='Dark Money The Hidden History of the Billionaires Behind the Rise of the Radical Right by Jane Mayer' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a></span>
  <span id="freeText10543556868986400556" style="display:none">Devastating critique of Bush/Cheney's deranged emotional response to 9/11. Clarifies not just the abject illegality and anti-Americanism of torture, but also its ineffectiveness and dangerous consequences. The book is not as tightly written as Mayer's subsequent "Dark" work: <br><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/27833494.Dark_Money_The_Hidden_History_of_the_Billionaires_Behind_the_Rise_of_the_Radical_Right" title="Dark Money The Hidden History of the Billionaires Behind the Rise of the Radical Right by Jane Mayer" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1452601408l/27833494._SY75_.jpg" alt="Dark Money The Hidden History of the Billionaires Behind the Rise of the Radical Right by Jane Mayer" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="10543556868986400556" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


